-- (INVESTIGATION_KEY). 255 reads neither CONDITION_KEY nor INVESTIGATION_KEY
-- off notification_event (it joins on patient_key only, line 1525), so any
-- valid FK value satisfies the constraint. We resolve both from existing rows
-- so the INSERT is robust on a fresh baseline (CONDITION is populated at
-- runtime; we take the lowest existing key; INVESTIGATION_KEY 1 is the
-- baseline sentinel row).
